    {
      "start_time": 612,
      "end_time": 616,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Welmo raps. I get up, I take a breath, I follow the rhythm, I clear my head in the blood of a race that looks in the mirror with black hands, hands that throw themselves onto the leather. Song, dance, rhythm. Song, dance, rhythm."
