    {
      "start_time": 836,
      "end_time": 842,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Ramón M. Gomez. This is the famous story of this couple who came from the Lesser Antilles and settled in Ponce. It's about a woman named Ana and how they started playing music."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
