    {
      "start_time": 888,
      "end_time": 1008,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "\"Plena De San Anton\" performed by Los Pleneros de la 21 and Michael Stuart. The original composer was Chago Montes.",
              "bold": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Chorus",
              "bold": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "The plena that I know is not from China, nor from Japan, because the plena comes from Ponce, from the San Antón neighborhood."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Because the plena comes from Ponce, from the San Antón neighborhood."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Verses",
              "bold": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Some say it's from Guayama and others that it's from Bayamón."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "But the plena comes from Ponce, from the San Antón neighborhood. But the plena comes from Ponce, from the San Antón neighborhood."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
